- Note : **Password for New Instructors and Students:**  
   The default password for newly created teacher and student accounts is set to their **ID**.  
   - Example: If the StudentID is **MTBI/23/DIT/001**, the password would be **MTBI/23/DIT/001**.
   - And the username is the StudentID and InstructorID. 